                    <div class="common-banner-title">
                        <img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/css/storage@2x.png" />
                        <h2>Azure 存档存储<span>Azure Archive Storage</span></h2>
                        <h4>在存储不常访问的数据方面具有优势的行业价格</h4>
                        <em><a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="home_site_trial_storage-blobs">申请试用<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></em>
